{"tid":2308279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師陳惠源: 法庭究竟係咪要對毫無資源嘅聽障被告如此苛刻 但對有無限資源嘅控方就如此寬鬆？","createTime":"2020-12-01T18:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T02:03:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1697f723c67c48e60d7c4d7552834b17ceb83e05","tid":2308279,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:23:05.000Z","msg":"裁判官鄭紀航不信羅鎮傑在盤問下聽錯問題，最終裁定他襲警罪成。有律師指，上訴庭會審視盤問的前文後理，判斷聽障是否被告轉變答案的唯一原因，並反問法庭「究竟係咪要對毫無資源嘅被告如此苛刻，但對有無限資源嘅控方就如此寬鬆？」有大律師指，上訴時可向法院引入新證據證明被告聽錯問題，如聽力學家報告。<br />\n<br />\n律師陳惠源指上訴庭不容易接納新證據，主要會考慮原審法官裁決是否有不安全、不穩妥的地方，如盤問的前文後理，法庭必須審視聽障是否被告突然轉變答案的唯一原因，「法官要有兩個唔信：一，唔信佢盤問聽錯；二，唔信佢覆問講真話。點解會有呢兩個唔信？邏輯上點理解？」陳反問：「究竟係咪要對毫無資源嘅被告如此苛刻，但對有無限資源嘅控方就如此寬鬆？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/JVPIEIMRQFFA5PXJWEXFJ6O7LA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FJVPIEIMRQFFA5PXJWEXFJ6O7LA%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2YlS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=d87e08c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FJVPIEIMRQFFA5PXJWEXFJ6O7LA%2F&h=ee4fb1fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/JVPIEIMRQFFA5PXJWEXFJ6O7LA/</a>"},{"pid":"6af01fe30f499008e511499b8af7fb85e136020c","tid":2308279,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff4a64d8b9d833f809d47b928574f06ea028a84","tid":2308279,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"盲官黑帝"},{"pid":"27e184caf95b98da5d811f63ec15949bc5ff2a0a","tid":2308279,"uid":236368,"like":1,"d